# Gitmoji + Conventional Commit Template
# Pick ONE gitmoji and uncomment it:
# ✨  feat:     new feature
# 🐛  fix:      bug fix
# ♻️  refactor: refactor code
# 🧹  chore:    tooling / config / deps
# 📝  docs:     documentation
# 🧪  test:     tests
# 🌐  i18n:     localisation/internationalisation

🌐 feat(scope): short description here

# Body (what & why, not how)
# - Detail 1
# - Detail 2

# Footer (optional: tickets, breaking changes)
# BREAKING CHANGE: ...
# Closes SKY-1234
